{
  "stem": "20684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 18,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told me lots of things about my father which I didn't know, even a few years ago when I was a Israel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And not all that good, some of them, but he was a bit of a devil.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think I must have taken it from him, taken some shortcuts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyhow, that's that-- when he was young, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was a devil.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, and they said that he was-- they used to tell me because he knew him-- he went to school with him on so on-- that he was a bit of a womanizer.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in France, he-- he lost his ways a few times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He spent eight years studying in-- medicine in France [INAUDIBLE] and he sort of did a few-- did a few naughty things that everybody does but you don't think your father does.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's god.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Your father wouldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He jumped out of windows and things like that they told me when husbands get home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] also the things [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They weren't together, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were in Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], they all come from Russia, these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very few survived in Poland and so this was sort of-- and we-- we made arrangements to go to-- to run away from Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went to Czechoslovakia, we got caught; we finished up in jail for a few days; we were bought out by Joint, which is an American Jewish foundation that bought us out; and we finished up going to Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
